    "Reward on the basis of number of publications favors, all other things being equal, publishing least-publishable-unitssplitting the totality of one's results into smaller bits to augment publication numbers -and/or repackaging the same data for different purposes and venues.",
    "It also favors having a large number of coauthors per paper, with authorship becoming gifts to be exchanged.",
